### `ingredients` Table

| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| ingredient_id | uuid | Primary key, auto-generated |
| ingredient_name | text | Common name |
| inci_name | text | Standardized INCI name — **critical matching key** |
| impact_score | text | Stored labels: `(-2)`, `(-1)`, `(0)`, `(+1)`, `(+2)` (nullable); scoring treats these as numeric -2 … +2 |
| classification | text | Beneficial / Harmful / Neutral / No Data (nullable) |
| plain_english_summary | text | One-sentence user-facing explanation (nullable) |
| study_title | text | Supporting clinical study title (nullable) |
| pubmed_link | text | URL to PubMed study (nullable) |
| year_published | integer | Year of publication (nullable) |
| evidence_strength | text | Strong / Moderate / Weak (nullable) |
| conflicting_evidence | text | Yes / No (nullable) |
| notes | text | Researcher flags or additional notes (nullable) |

> **Note:** `ingredient_id`, `ingredient_name`, and `inci_name` are required. All other columns are nullable pending data from the biomedical research scientist.

